title: Why "Winning" Isn't Enough, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO300
itunes:title: Why "Winning" Isn't Enough, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO300
description: Just "winning" isn't enough. "Winning" doesn't earn you glory or the right to brag. You have to DOMINATE. That's the mentality you have to have to truly be successful on an elite level...& this isn't an ego thing, either. It's not about just trying to prove you are way better than somebody else. It's not about feeling good because you decimated your competition. It actually has to do with YOU...your potential..& whether or not you die feeling proud of how you lived.
